@startuml
actor "Player" as P
participant "Paper Plugin" as Plugin
participant "Next.js API" as API
database "Database" as DB

P -> Plugin : Joins server / kills / events
Plugin -> API : POST /servers/:id/players/sync
API -> DB : Create/Update player entry
DB --> API : Return success
API --> Plugin : 200 OK

Plugin -> API : POST /servers/:id/players/:uuid/stats
API -> DB : Update player stats
DB --> API : Return success
API --> Plugin : 200 OK
@enduml
